OL,6,FThe steel giant has said the
OL,7,Frestructuring proposals are necessary
OL,8,Fto stem financial loses of up to #1
OL,9,Fmillion a day.
OL,11,FIt is expected nearly 3000 people will
OL,12,Flose their jobs when Blast Furnace 4
OL,13,Fshuts and the heavy-end assests are
OL,14,Fwound down later this year.
OL,16,FTata Steel says it is investing #1.25
OL,17,Fbillion and is committed to building
OL,18,Fan electric arc furnace as part of a
OL,19,Ftransition to low-CO2 steelmaking.
